remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f9ccc-104">Le proprietà di lettura / scrittura di una classe sono contrassegnate con il <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationAttribute> attributo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9ccc-104">The read-write properties of a class are marked with the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationAttribute> attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f9ccc-105">Inoltre, ogni proprietà di lettura / scrittura può essere uno dei due tipi: <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.Apply> o <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.OnCommit>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9ccc-105">In addition, each read-write property can be one of two types: <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.Apply> or <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.OnCommit>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f9ccc-106">Se una classe dispone di proprietà di lettura / scrittura che sono configurate come OnCommit, la classe deve avere un metodo contrassegnato dall'attributo ManagementCommit.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9ccc-106">If a class has read-write properties that are configured as OnCommit, the class should have a method that is marked with the ManagementCommit attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f9ccc-107">Quando sono state impostate tutte le proprietà OnCommit, verrà chiamato il metodo associato.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9ccc-107">The associated method will be called when all OnCommit properties have been set.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f9ccc-108">Il metodo contrassegnato come non è thread-safe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9ccc-108">The marked method is not thread safe.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f9ccc-109">Se nessun metodo è contrassegnato con l'attributo ManagementCommit, la classe gestisce gli aggiornamenti della configurazione da sola senza alcuna indicazione che l'aggiornamento è stata completata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9ccc-109">If no method is marked with the ManagementCommit attribute, the class manages the configuration updates by itself without any indication that the update has completed.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f9ccc-110">Il metodo contrassegnato dall'attributo ManagementCommit non accetta parametri e ha un tipo restituito void.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f9ccc-110">The method marked with the ManagementCommit attribute does not take any parameters and it has a void return type.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
public class Process  
{  
    /// Key attribute marks a key property. Keys are not changeable.  
    /// Keys have to be unique information.  
    [ManagementKey]  
    public int Id   
    {  
        get {    }  
    }  
  
    /// ManagementConfiguration stands for read/write manageable  
    /// property from a read/write field.  
    [ManagementConfiguration]  
    public string UserDefinedString;  
  
    [ManagementCommit]  
    void SaveOnDevice();  
}  
```
